Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.74,0:00:22.94,特效,,0,0,0,,武当道观 中国南部
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.18,0:02:58.90,特效,,0,0,0,,马可波罗圣诞特辑
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.32,0:02:58.61,特效,,0,0,0,,百  眼
Dialogue: 0,0:26:04.20,0:26:08.54,特效,,0,0,0,,马可波罗第二季
Dialogue: 0,0:26:04.29,0:26:08.50,特效,,0,0,0,,2016年 夏季
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.98,0:00:33.96,对白,,0,0,0,,李金宝\NLi Jinbao.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.13,0:00:35.63,对白,,0,0,0,,蒙古人\NMongols.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.94,0:00:38.57,对白,,0,0,0,,他们已经把北峰的道观毁了\NThey have already destroyed the temple at North Peak.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.14,0:00:42.66,对白,,0,0,0,,- 尼姑们在哪？ - 东面的道观里\N- Where are the nuns?  - In the cloisters. East.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.38,0:00:46.64,对白,,0,0,0,,记住我们的誓约 战斗到底\NRemember the oath. We fight to the end.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.05,0:00:48.96,对白,,0,0,0,,得道之人 视生死为一条\NLife and death are one thread.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.75,0:00:51.67,对白,,0,0,0,,我会保护经卷的\NI will guard the scrolls.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.99,0:02:31.61,对白,,0,0,0,,李金宝\NLi Jinbao!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.94,0:02:41.27,对白,,0,0,0,,别杀他\NDo not kill him.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.77,0:02:44.57,对白,,0,0,0,,大汗会要这个人的\NThe Khan will want this one.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.25,0:03:19.24,对白,,0,0,0,,什么样的道士能够只身杀死\NWhat kind of monk is able to kill,by himself,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.86,0:03:21.99,对白,,0,0,0,,我二十五个蒙古勇士\N25 Mongol soldiers?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.44,0:03:27.23,对白,,0,0,0,,是在你道观里练成的歪门邪术吗\NIs it a form of dark magic practiced at your temple?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.86,0:03:30.60,对白,,0,0,0,,你永远不会知道的 明白吗\NYou shall never know, shall you?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.84,0:03:33.13,对白,,0,0,0,,你刚才说什么 道士\NWhat did you just say, monk?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.18,0:03:34.81,对白,,0,0,0,,你毁坏道观\NYou destroyed a temple
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.12,0:03:36.23,对白,,0,0,0,,你所寻求的答案\Nand all of the ancient
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.23,0:03:38.36,对白,,0,0,0,,那些古老经卷都被毁掉了\Nscrolls that contained the answers you seek.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.42,0:03:42.55,对白,,0,0,0,,你们这些道士给我南方的敌人提供庇护\NYou monks were offering shelter to my enemies in South China.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.77,0:03:45.89,对白,,0,0,0,,没有人可以藐视可汗\NNo place defies the Khan.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.77,0:03:48.14,对白,,0,0,0,,我再问你一遍\NI will ask you again.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.21,0:03:50.66,对白,,0,0,0,,如果你不说 就拔掉你的舌头\NIf you hold your tongue, I will take your tongue.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.77,0:03:54.06,对白,,0,0,0,,道观里到底有什么战斗秘诀\NWhat is this fighting art kept secret in a mountain temple?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.47,0:03:58.36,对白,,0,0,0,,平和的艺术\NThe art of peace.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.38,0:04:01.94,对白,,0,0,0,,你弄断训练精良的士兵的脖子\NYou break the necks of trained soldiers,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.16,0:04:05.97,对白,,0,0,0,,割开他们的喉咙 像对野猪一样开肠破肚\Ncut their throats, gut them like wild pigs,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.31,0:04:07.58,对白,,0,0,0,,还说是平和\Nand you call it peace?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.62,0:04:11.51,对白,,0,0,0,,你毁掉道观 还说是天数已定\NYou destroy a temple and call it destiny?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.64,0:04:17.73,对白,,0,0,0,,过去的君王可不曾有我这般慈悲\NKings of the past would not have shown you grace.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.25,0:04:21.73,对白,,0,0,0,,我 要发动战争的时候\NMe, when I make war on a city,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.27,0:04:24.32,对白,,0,0,0,,会留所有的工匠一命\NI allow the craftsmen to live.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.81,0:04:28.97,对白,,0,0,0,,我会征他们入伍 继续生活\NI conscript them into service... and they live.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.75,0:04:30.97,对白,,0,0,0,,就在这里\NHere.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.62,0:04:37.92,对白,,0,0,0,,你要给我的战将讲一下那些汉人的秘诀\NYou will reveal these Chinese secrets to my war ministers.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.06,0:04:43.40,对白,,0,0,0,,用汉人的绝招 去攻击汉人\NReveal Chinese secrets... to fight the Chinese.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.34,0:04:50.01,对白,,0,0,0,,证明自己有用 就留你一命\NProve yourself useful, you can live.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.51,0:04:52.40,对白,,0,0,0,,违反我的规矩\NDefy my laws...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.95,0:04:56.08,对白,,0,0,0,,就让你死得 比那些和经卷共同消失的道士\Nyou'll die a death far worse than that suffered by the monks
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.12,0:04:58.21,对白,,0,0,0,,凄惨百倍\Nwho perished with your scrolls.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.60,0:05:05.01,对白,,0,0,0,,觉得我下令时候很幽默吗\NOh, you find humor in my decree?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.27,0:05:08.34,对白,,0,0,0,,至高的刽子手只有一个\NThere is only one Supreme Executioner.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.49,0:05:11.42,对白,,0,0,0,,那些想要抢占他位置的人\NAnd those who try to take his place
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.43,0:05:15.38,对白,,0,0,0,,就好像小孩子 模仿手艺精湛的木匠砍树\Nare like children trying to carve wood as a master carpenter.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.25,0:05:19.11,对白,,0,0,0,,多数人都会伤到自己的手\NMost will injure their own hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.90,0:05:22.40,对白,,0,0,0,,你不怕死吗\NYou do not fear death?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.64,0:05:25.36,对白,,0,0,0,,不会苟且偷生\NI do not cling to life.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.28,0:05:28.16,对白,,0,0,0,,二者大不相同\NThere is a difference.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.10,0:05:34.53,对白,,0,0,0,,带他下去\NRemove him.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.08,0:05:48.93,对白,,0,0,0,,这位摔跤手外号草原黑野猪\NThis wrestler is named Black Steppe Boar.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.40,0:05:52.30,对白,,0,0,0,,是在塞西亚抓到的犯人\NA prisoner captured in Scythia.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.25,0:05:56.29,对白,,0,0,0,,知道为什么要给他个野猪的外号吗\NDo you know why he is named after the boar?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.53,0:05:58.75,对白,,0,0,0,,他们很是相像嘛\NHis resemblance is extraordinary.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.27,0:06:01.12,对白,,0,0,0,,叫他野猪是因为\NHe is called Boar because
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.16,0:06:04.86,对白,,0,0,0,,他赤手空拳 杀人无数\Nhe has killed such without a weapon many times.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.40,0:06:10.01,对白,,0,0,0,,野猪先动手 他会锁住你\NBoar will advance. He will seize you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.77,0:06:13.88,对白,,0,0,0,,你来展示下如何突破控制\NYou will demonstrate how to break the grasp.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.49,0:06:21.08,对白,,0,0,0,,还要蒙住我的眼\NYou cover my eyes?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.53,0:06:23.00,对白,,0,0,0,,就这些吗\NIs that just?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.51,0:06:28.32,对白,,0,0,0,,大汗想知道你蒙住眼之后要怎么动手\NThe Great Khan wants a report on how you fight blindfolded.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.79,0:06:31.03,对白,,0,0,0,,真是个任性的傻瓜\NHe is a most capricious fool.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.22,0:06:33.75,对白,,0,0,0,,你要不是懦夫 就把这话当面传达给他\NAnd if you were not cowards, you would tell him the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.86,0:06:35.41,对白,,0,0,0,,闭嘴 臭道士\NQuiet, monk!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.63,0:08:52.86,对白,,0,0,0,,你杀的那个将军是速不台的儿子\NThe general you killed was the son of Subutai.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.54,0:08:56.38,对白,,0,0,0,,知道这个名字吗 道士\NDo you know that name, monk?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.47,0:08:58.89,对白,,0,0,0,,不知道\NI do not.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.34,0:09:03.26,对白,,0,0,0,,曾经效忠成吉思汗的 最伟大的军事将领\NGreatest military commander ever to serve Genghis Khan.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.63,0:09:05.47,对白,,0,0,0,,你杀了他儿子\NYou slayed his son.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.79,0:09:08.17,对白,,0,0,0,,这是罪上加罪\NThis is a crime beyond crimes.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.78,0:09:11.80,对白,,0,0,0,,但是\NYet...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.38,0:09:16.82,对白,,0,0,0,,就像你说的 不会苟且偷生\Nyou do not cling to life, as you say.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.04,0:09:21.08,对白,,0,0,0,,死意味着一切皆无\NDeath means nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.86,0:09:26.71,对白,,0,0,0,,一个可汗该怎么做？\NWhat is a Khan to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.67,0:09:40.06,对白,,0,0,0,,曾经有商人从小亚美尼亚给我带来一只白鹤\NA merchant once gifted me a white crane from Lesser Armenia...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.50,0:09:43.95,对白,,0,0,0,,一种极其罕见的水鸟\Na water bird that was most uncommon...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.32,0:09:48.04,对白,,0,0,0,,因为它生下来时候全黑\Nbecause it had been born all black.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.52,0:09:52.25,对白,,0,0,0,,黑身白鹤\NBlack white crane.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.86,0:09:59.28,对白,,0,0,0,,我知道这是吉兆\NI knew it was an auspicious
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.32,0:10:01.78,对白,,0,0,0,,能给我带来好运 但是\Nbeing that would bring me fortune, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.84,0:10:06.73,对白,,0,0,0,,这只白鹤不愿意待在我的湖里\Nthat black white crane refused to stay on my lake.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.91,0:10:10.94,对白,,0,0,0,,总是想飞走\NAlways, it would fly away.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.95,0:10:15.61,对白,,0,0,0,,自然的呼唤而已 你也明白\NJust its natural calling, you see.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.80,0:10:19.76,对白,,0,0,0,,所以\NSo...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.10,0:10:25.58,对白,,0,0,0,,为了保留它和我的好运\NI served him and my fortune...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.23,0:10:29.32,对白,,0,0,0,,就砍掉了它一只翅膀\Nby cutting one wing.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.74,0:10:32.74,对白,,0,0,0,,奉天承运\N"By law of the Grand Khan,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.87,0:10:33.95,对白,,0,0,0,,皇帝诏曰\NLord of Lords..."
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.99,0:10:36.47,对白,,0,0,0,,你以为我为什么要让你蒙眼搏斗\NWhy do you think I had you fight blindfolded?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.36,0:10:39.58,对白,,0,0,0,,就因为我是任性的傻瓜？\NBecause I'm a capricious fool?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.54,0:10:41.87,对白,,0,0,0,,还是想看看你\NOr to see if you are capable
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.89,0:10:44.77,对白,,0,0,0,,道家的绝技 能不能在黑暗中战斗\Nof your Taoist secrets and skills while in the dark?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.10,0:10:46.36,对白,,0,0,0,,钦此\N"So be it."
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.60,0:10:49.37,对白,,0,0,0,,因为我知道把你带上来的时候\NBecause I knew the moment you were presented,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.74,0:10:52.65,对白,,0,0,0,,肯定不会像一个顺从的画师\Nyou would not be like the obedient painter...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.35,0:10:58.26,对白,,0,0,0,,听话的占星术士 满足于饮酒作乐的诗人\Nthe resigned astrologer, the noble poet contented with wine.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.37,0:11:03.12,对白,,0,0,0,,你会拒绝服侍蒙古帝国\NYou would refuse to serve the Mongol Empire.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.84,0:11:09.33,对白,,0,0,0,,到今天\NTo this day...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.23,0:11:13.80,对白,,0,0,0,,白鹤依旧留在我的湖边\Nthat black white crane remains on my lake.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.21,0:11:16.67,对白,,0,0,0,,它是我的\NHe is mine...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.72,0:11:19.47,对白,,0,0,0,,我心所爱\Nand he is beloved.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.31,0:16:24.90,对白,,0,0,0,,现在准备好\NAre you now ready...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.09,0:16:28.65,对白,,0,0,0,,向我的战将传授技艺了吗？\Nto teach my Ministers of Warfare?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.50,0:16:34.99,对白,,0,0,0,,给道士上茶\NTea for the monk.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.18,0:16:41.79,对白,,0,0,0,,不要把我和你那些神圣的和尚混为一谈\NDo not confuse me with one of your holy Buddhists.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.57,0:16:44.89,对白,,0,0,0,,是酒\NWine.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.33,0:17:05.61,对白,,0,0,0,,你因为杀速不台的儿子接受了惩罚\NYou were punished for killing the son of Subutai.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.03,0:17:07.66,对白,,0,0,0,,永远别忘了\NNever forget that.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.07,0:17:09.59,对白,,0,0,0,,不会的\NI shall not.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.00,0:17:11.35,对白,,0,0,0,,武当的道士\NThe monks of Wudang
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.46,0:17:14.96,对白,,0,0,0,,花费毕生的精力要达到真正的虚空\Nspend their lives trying to achieve true emptiness.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.87,0:17:18.68,对白,,0,0,0,,但只有当他克服这种虚空\NFor only when the sage can overcome the self
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.92,0:17:21.05,对白,,0,0,0,,方能入道\Ndoes he enter into the Tao.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.90,0:17:26.08,对白,,0,0,0,,这是所有秘密中最为终极的一个\NThat is a dark mystery beyond all mysteries,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.53,0:17:28.96,对白,,0,0,0,,也是你给我的礼物\Nand a gift you gave to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.22,0:17:30.46,对白,,0,0,0,,失明\NBlind?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.87,0:17:36.31,对白,,0,0,0,,现在我能用一百只眼 看这个世界\NI now see the world with one hundred eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.31,0:17:52.83,对白,,0,0,0,,再给他倒酒\NGive him more wine.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.48,0:18:09.66,对白,,0,0,0,,我刚吃了你的马\NI've just captured your horse.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.50,0:18:12.79,对白,,0,0,0,,我知道\NI know.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.40,0:18:14.88,对白,,0,0,0,,那你还要知道\NThen know this.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.48,0:18:18.13,对白,,0,0,0,,那里有四座道观\NThere are four Taoist temples
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.14,0:18:20.77,对白,,0,0,0,,依旧站立在武当山上\Nstill standing in the Wudang Mountains.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.48,0:18:26.27,对白,,0,0,0,,我的人半个月之后会去将其焚烧 夷为平地\NMy men will go there in a fortnight and burn them to the ground.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.14,0:18:29.13,对白,,0,0,0,,我一声令下\NAt my single command,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.38,0:18:32.96,对白,,0,0,0,,你的宗教就会从这世界上消失\Nyour religion can be wiped off the face of this earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.18,0:18:36.90,对白,,0,0,0,,亦或 它能生存\NOr it can live...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.99,0:18:40.12,对白,,0,0,0,,成长\Ngrow...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.45,0:18:42.74,对白,,0,0,0,,繁荣\Nthrive...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.37,0:18:45.51,对白,,0,0,0,,只要你向我证明它的价值\Nif you prove its value to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.46,0:18:48.48,对白,,0,0,0,,就是训练你的战将？\NBy training your ministers?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.75,0:18:52.13,对白,,0,0,0,,还有别人\NAnd someone else.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.46,0:19:13.48,对白,,0,0,0,,您一定就是王子了\NYou must be the prince.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.25,0:19:16.51,对白,,0,0,0,,我叫阿尔泰\NI am called Altai.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.48,0:19:19.11,对白,,0,0,0,,你为何而来？\NWhy are you here?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.88,0:19:21.03,对白,,0,0,0,,上课\NLessons.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.96,0:19:25.05,对白,,0,0,0,,你要在这些课里\NAnd what do you intend to teach me
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.37,0:19:28.05,对白,,0,0,0,,教我什么？\Nin these... lessons?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.46,0:19:32.74,对白,,0,0,0,,我要让你知道 即使是可汗家的儿子\NI'm here to teach you that even the son of a royal khan
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.83,0:19:35.53,对白,,0,0,0,,也能谦卑 向人求教\Nis capable of humility and learning.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.03,0:19:39.75,对白,,0,0,0,,把扫帚拿起来 阿尔泰 给我扫地\NThen take the broom, Altai, and sweep my floor.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.64,0:19:49.36,对白,,0,0,0,,回答不错 只要你能坚持\NGood answer. If only you believed it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.51,0:20:06.07,对白,,0,0,0,,你就是这大千世界花园里的一个流浪的种子\NYou are a little nomad weed in the garden of the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.35,0:20:11.05,对白,,0,0,0,,他们希望你长成参天大树\NThey wish you to grow into a flowering tree.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.03,0:20:19.92,对白,,0,0,0,,这样的树最重要的是什么\NWhat is the most important part of such a tree?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.07,0:20:23.86,对白,,0,0,0,,众多的分支和开花\NThe many branches and the flowering.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.22,0:20:26.01,对白,,0,0,0,,我说的是传承\NI speak of legacy.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.25,0:20:31.33,对白,,0,0,0,,啊 谢谢你讲解这个晦涩的比喻\NAh! Thank you for untangling your elusive metaphor.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.20,0:20:37.60,对白,,0,0,0,,我们从根开始\NWe begin with roots.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.73,0:21:27.44,对白,,0,0,0,,可以问个问题吗？\NMay I ask a question?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.51,0:21:28.53,对白,,0,0,0,,问\NDo.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.18,0:21:33.25,对白,,0,0,0,,如果你要在墙上搞书法\NIf you wish calligraphy on your wall,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.60,0:21:35.86,对白,,0,0,0,,干嘛不叫个能看得见的匠人\Nwhy not summon a painter who can see?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.23,0:21:38.29,对白,,0,0,0,,能读懂我写的这个符号吗\NCan you not read the character I made?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.73,0:21:40.53,对白,,0,0,0,,是个火的标志\NIt is a symbol for fire.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.83,0:21:42.05,对白,,0,0,0,,有什么问题\NThen what is wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.60,0:21:45.72,对白,,0,0,0,,- 上下颠倒了  - 没错\N- It's upside down.  - Precisely.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.79,0:21:51.75,对白,,0,0,0,,这就是功夫耐性的特质 控制\NThis is the kung fu character for patience, control.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.05,0:21:54.70,对白,,0,0,0,,要把这个一直记在脑子里\NRemember this in the future, always,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.03,0:21:56.92,对白,,0,0,0,,永远不要屈服于怒气\N"Never give way to anger."
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.03,0:21:58.40,对白,,0,0,0,,师父\NSifu?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.16,0:22:03.42,对白,,0,0,0,,我的训练还没累到让你闭嘴吗？\NHave I not trained you into exhausted silence yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.40,0:22:07.99,对白,,0,0,0,,今天的课就到这里 王子殿下\NToday's lesson is done, My Radiant Highness.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.25,0:22:46.14,对白,,0,0,0,,你看不见 我知道 但是\NYou cannot see it, I know. But...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.42,0:22:52.18,对白,,0,0,0,,我向你保证这是一个伟大的汉人工匠\NI assure you it has been overseen by a great Chinese architect...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.20,0:22:59.12,对白,,0,0,0,,用最珍贵的木材和技艺打造而成\Nmade from the most precious of woods and hides, and--
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.16,0:23:03.79,对白,,0,0,0,,愚蠢\NImbecile.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.97,0:23:08.75,对白,,0,0,0,,谁把这个火字倒着写在这里的\NSomeone has painted the character of fire upside down.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.12,0:23:10.26,对白,,0,0,0,,我写的\NI did.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.73,0:23:22.73,对白,,0,0,0,,趁着新年这一天\NOn this day of the New Year...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.95,0:23:28.21,对白,,0,0,0,,我把这第四宝堂\NI ordain this place the Hall of the Fourth Treasure.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.97,0:23:32.81,对白,,0,0,0,,用你百眼的名字命名\NI name you Hundred Eyes...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.95,0:23:36.23,对白,,0,0,0,,武术大臣\N...Minister of Martial Affairs.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.55,0:23:38.90,对白,,0,0,0,,还有\NAnd so...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.88,0:23:43.68,对白,,0,0,0,,我请你 以武当道士的身份\NI ask of you, as a Wudang priest,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.62,0:23:47.00,对白,,0,0,0,,给我儿子一个汉人名字\Ngive my son his Chinese name.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.29,0:23:52.71,对白,,0,0,0,,史上有五百多回\NThere have been 500 over time
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.47,0:23:56.36,对白,,0,0,0,,有人号称权倾中华大地\Nwho have held the name Emperor of All China,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.79,0:23:58.95,对白,,0,0,0,,天之子\NSon of Heaven.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.03,0:24:02.56,对白,,0,0,0,,以血受戒\NOrdained by blood,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.79,0:24:03.82,对白,,0,0,0,,这些人恐怕\Nthere are those who would
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.86,0:24:06.47,对白,,0,0,0,,更适合去收拾牛粪\Nhave been better suited to harvest cow dung
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.86,0:24:09.74,对白,,0,0,0,,而不是掌控这个伟大的帝国\Nthan to rule the greatest empire on earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.03,0:24:13.25,对白,,0,0,0,,还些类似白银\NThere are those who were as silver,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.42,0:24:16.58,对白,,0,0,0,,一种稀有金属 但比货币值钱\Na lesser metal, but worthy of coinage.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.23,0:24:19.36,对白,,0,0,0,,还有些人\NAnd then there are those...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.12,0:24:21.95,对白,,0,0,0,,像冰冷的石头\Nlike cold stone,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.40,0:24:24.99,对白,,0,0,0,,会抑制自己的力量和怒气\Nwho force their strength and fury
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.25,0:24:29.17,对白,,0,0,0,,得到的却是胆小怕事的名号\Nand win the title by fear and intimidation.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.23,0:24:32.97,对白,,0,0,0,,流血 不足为奇\NBlood is nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.60,0:24:37.01,对白,,0,0,0,,勇气和精神才成就贤哲\NHeart and spirit make the sage.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.05,0:24:41.48,对白,,0,0,0,,因此\NAnd by this...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:42.49,0:24:46.17,对白,,0,0,0,,我给这孩子取名为 真金\NI give this boy the name Jingim.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:48.88,0:24:50.64,对白,,0,0,0,,赤足真金\N"True gold."
Dialogue: 0,0:24:58.40,0:24:59.62,对白,,0,0,0,,那就这样\NSo be it.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:00.05,0:25:02.47,对白,,0,0,0,,以后他就叫这个名字\NHe will walk out of here with this name,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:02.88,0:25:04.49,对白,,0,0,0,,把它当成自己的名字\Nand carry it as his own
Dialogue: 0,0:25:04.53,0:25:07.82,对白,,0,0,0,,也只有那些真正的贤者明白\Ninto a tomorrow only the oracles can see.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:13.51,0:25:14.97,对白,,0,0,0,,至于你 道士\NAs for you, priest...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:17.71,0:25:19.68,对白,,0,0,0,,这殿堂是你的了\Nthis temple is yours.

